snippet.textDisplay: I don't know I just love Coke Studio and just really love QB but this song was not that wonder I expect from CS. It frankly sounded like din rather than an actual song. QB's voice and the beautiful CS instruments combine beautifully everytime to produce wonders. But this time the music was overpowering her voice which is completely off for a QB fan. I even liked Sammi Meri Vaar although people found it to be  not that good but still I loved QB's vocals there. But here it feels there's nothing for me to like. :-(
